headline: Emerson Electric (EMR): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Emerson Electric trades at $132.65 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 18.6% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 15.7%.
